{"tid":1667133,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黑狗淋病道歉 為免挑動全球穆斯林聚焦新疆","createTime":"2019-10-21T09:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T12:03:34.000Z","uid":998,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3b2d5398439c40f29d8727f1a6c519c0eacdbd3f","tid":1667133,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"就好似nba同blizzard <br />\n中共已經開左好多條戰線搞到好多西方國家民眾憎佢<br />\n如果連穆斯林都得罪埋，一帶一路可以死得，咁土共就得翻非洲。所以逼警畜同淋病出來道歉降溫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>但係林病連人地宗教規矩都唔尊重，就咁入去，等睇穆斯林社區有咩反映。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a888f42ccc8b9ff0211b841ffe64755083b56bf3","tid":1667133,"uid":998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:47:27.000Z","msg":"煲到全球穆斯林反共"},{"pid":"f7a32487fbad576bc6deed5ca512cb8a3e2a8b6e","tid":1667133,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:48:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bdb3f40b267e979c2b0497ef57c14c0c05c6fed","tid":1667133,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:49:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"32fe2ef8daeb8f3b7cd8e90a5a1357cbf57a5d79","tid":1667133,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:49:38.000Z","msg":"新彊集中營"},{"pid":"cfe9b120be651b8ef14b17fb5316a4c23688319b","tid":1667133,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:49:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bda44f0ab647fcaafeafed02a59ed7f6381b46d","tid":1667133,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:49:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">想贏嘅同我入嚟<br />\n快啲把握最好時機</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n係時候搞個 尊重宗教自由大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"faf1a56eadf4302cbcf3057b57c1c0e92906ac32","tid":1667133,"uid":91259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c